    "ACE2005 [56]ACE2005 dataset has been issued by LDC which involves Chines, English and Arabic training datasets.",
    "This dataset may be utilized for tasks like relation extraction and nested NER [9] and this dataset contains 145,000 English words with six entity types: time, location name, place, percentage, person name, and organization name for English.",
    "ACE2004 [56]ACE2004 dataset has been released by Language Data Consortium (LDC) which also contains Arabic, Chinese and English and in order to facilitate the automated analysis of textual representations of human language, this dataset attempts to create automatic content extraction tools.",
    "It may be utilized for NER's nested entity recognition.",
    "Performance metricPerformance metric is used for evaluation of experimental result and it's described in details with definition as well as Perfomance Metric Content Evaluation Precision Recall F-score Quality Evaluation Nonredundency Grammtically The entity generated by the NER system and the ground truth are identical.True Negative (True -ve): The NER system did not detect an entity that appeared in the ground truth."
